<h3>Why <%=@offer.user.firstname%> ?</h3>
<br>
<p><%= @offer.offer_description %></p>
<br>
<h3>Our santa disponibility: </h3>
<p><b>The <%= @offer.availability.to_time.strftime('%e %B %Y') %></b> in <%= @offer.location %></p>
